    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Nationality or culture of the kingdom of Saxony, the Prussian province of Saxony, or the state of Saxony in the German Democratic Republic, until 1952 when it was replaced as an administrative district by Leipzig, Karl-Marx-Stadt, and Dresden. For the ancient Saxon culture, use "Saxon (historical culture or style)."</Note_Text>
